# JJFB / GWY Launcher Shim Rules

## Project Goal

This project is NOT about recreating or redesigning the UI of the game "机甲风暴".

The goal is:

- emulate the launch behavior of the Maopao/GWY online-game shell;
- bypass the forced-update blocker of the GWY shell;
- reconstruct the `startGame/runapp` launch contract for `gwy/jjfb.mrp`;
- keep the original game files unchanged;
- allow the original `gwy/jjfb.mrp` to run naturally.

Main route:

```text
GWY shell launch chain
→ cfg index=36
→ startGame / runapp
→ correct cwd/root/resource root
→ load gwy/jjfb.mrp
→ mrc_loader.ext
→ robotol.ext
→ original game self-runs
```

---

## Hard Rules

### 1. Do not modify original game logic

Never modify the logic of:

```text
gwy/jjfb.mrp
robotol.ext
mrc_loader.ext
```

Do not patch game behavior unless explicitly marked as a temporary diagnostic probe.

### 2. Do not fake game UI

Forbidden as official solution:

```text
host overlay UI
fake slogo
fake loadingbar
fake progress animation
fake text/status messages
manually drawing game UI
```

The UI must come from the original game resources and original game flow.

### 3. Do not use internal game-state forcing as final solution

Forbidden as official solution:

```text
force ui_mode=0x45
manual AC8 write
manual progress_count write
progress driver
manual 0x2EF86C tail jump
```

These may only be used as temporary probes and must be clearly labeled as probes.

### 4. Do not treat v43-v48 splash experiments as the main route

The previous splash/UI work is diagnostic only.  
Do not keep optimizing:

```text
slogo position
loadingbar position
chrome details
310BB4 pixel-perfect behavior
2EC6B0 UI behavior
```

unless it directly affects the GWY launcher shim.

---

## Correct Main Route

### Build GWY Launcher Shim

Create/maintain a mode:

```text
JJFB_GWY_LAUNCHER_MODE=1
```

This mode should:

```text
1. avoid entering the GWY shell UI;
2. avoid the GWY forced-update blocker;
3. simulate the post-update/no-update state of the GWY shell;
4. use cfg index=36;
5. pass the exact game launch parameters;
6. set correct cwd/root/resource root;
7. load the original gwy/jjfb.mrp;
8. allow mrc_loader.ext and robotol.ext to run naturally.
```

---

## cfg index=36 Contract

Known game entry:

```text
title    = 机甲风暴(火爆公测)
target   = gwy/jjfb.mrp
icon     = ng_jjfb.gif
napptype = 12
nextid   = 482
ncode    = 512
narg     = 0
narg1    = 1
nmrpname = gwy/jjfb.mrp
```

Required parameter string:

```text
napptype=12_nextid=482_ncode=512_narg=0_narg1=1_nmrpname=gwy/jjfb.mrp_gwyblink
```

This is the primary launch contract.

---

## Resource Root Rules

The complete GWY resource directory must be preserved.

Expected structure:

```text
game_files/
  mythroad/
    320x480/          # active pack (preferred)
      gwy/
        gifs/
        jjfbol/
        save/
        sound/
        ...
    240x320/          # legacy identical jjfb content
```

Path model:

```text
mythroad_root = game_files/mythroad/320x480
gwy_root      = game_files/mythroad/320x480/gwy
target_mrp    = game_files/mythroad/320x480/gwy/jjfb.mrp
```

Guest path mapping must support:

```text
gwy/jjfb.mrp
gwy/jjfbol/...
gwy/gifs/...
gwy/save/...
gwy/sound/...
```

If startup/UI/resources are abnormal, check `FILEOPEN_MISS` and path mapping first.

