Avoid noisy logs:

```text
per-character string xref logs
every SPLASH_ENTER
pixel dumps
unbounded 2EC6B0 dumps
loadingbar character-by-character traces
```

---

## File Open Trace Requirement

Every important file open must resolve guest path to host path:

```text
[JJFB_FILEOPEN] guest="gwy/jjfb.mrp" host="...\240x320\gwy\jjfb.mrp" ok=1 pc=... lr=...
[JJFB_FILEOPEN] guest="gwy/jjfbol/..." host="...\240x320\gwy\jjfbol\..." ok=1/0 pc=... lr=...
[JJFB_FILEOPEN_MISS] guest="..." tried=[...] pc=... lr=...
```

Large numbers of misses mean the root/path mapping is wrong.

