```

---

## Update Layer Distinction

Always distinguish two update layers:

### GWY shell forced update

```text
gwy/gbrwcore/gamelist/vdload shell update
```

This is the blocker to bypass or simulate as already passed.

### JJFB game self update/check

```text
jjfb.mrp internal check/update/login/network flow
```

Do not bypass as the official solution. Let the original game handle it.

