## Docs / Reports / Packages (opt-in)

Do **not** create these every round by default:

```text
reports/vXX_*.md
README/01_HANDOFF_CONTEXT/LATEST_DIRECTION_*.md
packages/JJFB_vXX_*.zip
```

Only write markdown reports, handoff direction docs, or zip packages when the user **explicitly** asks (e.g. “写报告”“打包”“出 vXX 文档”).

Allowed without asking:

```text
code / scripts needed to advance the launch chain
RUN_*.ps1 when useful to reproduce a run
logs/*.txt produced by running the app (runtime evidence)
```

When the user does ask for a report, include:

```text
1. goal
2. modified files
3. new env vars
4. run command
5. key logs
6. conclusion
7. disproved assumptions
8. current blocker
9. next minimal task
```

